<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
      <% if (error && error.length) { %>
        <div class="flash-box flash-error">
          <span><%= error[0] %></span>
          <button class="flash-close" onclick="this.parentElement.style.display='none';">&times;</button>
        </div>
      <% } %>
      
      <% if (success && success.length) { %>
        <div class="flash-box flash-success">
          <span><%= success[0] %></span>
          <button class="flash-close" onclick="this.parentElement.style.display='none';">&times;</button>
        </div>
      <% } %>   
        <h1>Welcome to Phertek!</h1>
        <p>Phertek is a health and finance digital product company dedicated to empowering individuals and businesses through innovative solutions and professional opportunities.</p>
        <p>For businesses, Phertek offers custom digital products designed to streamline operations in the healthcare and financial sectors, enhancing efficiency and accessibility.</p>
        <p>At Phertek, our mission is to bridge the gap between technology, finance, and healthcareâ€”ensuring that businesses thrive while individuals gain the resources and opportunities they need to succeed.</p>
        <p>Join us at one of our upcoming events to learn more about our products and services, network with industry professionals, and discover new opportunities for growth and development.</p>
        <h2>Our Events</h2>
        <p>Phertek offers four distinct event categories: Volunteer Events, Paid Events, Community Events, and Professional Events.</p>
        <p>Our events are designed to provide valuable resources, networking opportunities, and professional development for individuals and businesses in the healthcare and financial sectors.</p>
        <p>Register for an event today and take the first step toward a brighter future with Phertek!</p>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
<script>
  setTimeout(() => {
    const flash = document.querySelector('.flash-box');
    if (flash) flash.style.display = 'none';
  }, 4000);
</script>
</html>